      "descriptionModule": {
        "briefSummary": "Efficacy and safety of rosnilimab (ANB030) in subjects with moderate-to-severe Alopecia Areata",
        "detailedDescription": "This is a Phase 2, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled, parallel-group,multicenter study to evaluate the safety, tolerability, and efficacy of rosnilimab in subjects with alopecia areata (AA).This study also will evaluate the pharmacokinetics (PK) and pharmacodynamics (PD) of rosnilimab and evaluate the immunogenicity of rosnilimab in subjects with AA."
      },
